msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:68
msgid "/dev/dvb/adapter0/dvr0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:69
msgid "/dev/dvb/adapter0/frontend0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:71
msgid ""
"The ``/dev/dvb/adapter0/dvr0`` device node is used to read the MPEG2 Data "
"Stream and the ``/dev/dvb/adapter0/frontend0`` device node is used to tune "
"the frontend tuner module. The ``/dev/dvb/adapter0/demux0`` is used to "
"control what programs will be received."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:76
msgid ""
"Depending on the card's feature set, the Device Driver API could also expose "
"other device nodes:"
msgstr ""

