#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:81
msgid "/dev/dvb/adapter0/net0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:82
msgid "/dev/dvb/adapter0/osd0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:83
msgid "/dev/dvb/adapter0/video0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/dvb_intro.rst:85
msgid ""
"The ``/dev/dvb/adapter0/ca0`` is used to decode encrypted channels. The "
"other device nodes are found only on devices that use the av7110 driver, "
"with is now obsoleted, together with the extra API whose such devices use."
